This directory contains gyroscope Tool library.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
It provide gyroscope test item feature on PC side, which allow test gyroscope as GUI.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1. liblog

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. libft.so
2. libhwm.so
3. libnvram.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
============== 
Files in this directory is used to generate a library which's name is 'libmeta_gyroscope'.
libmeta_gyroscope.a provides API that will get sensor data from driver.


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..

